Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:40.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152.304,141.492)\org(1152.291,141.492)\fscx98.651\fscy100\frz0.684\fry-3.364\frx0\fax0\fnArial\fs42\b1\xbord3.85\ybord3.9\c&H2E2216&\3c&H847A6E&}Become World Dai Stars together!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.40,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,The two of us together!
